---

{% from "components/eesti-isikukood-input/macro.njk" import eestiIsikukoodInput %}
{% from "components/label/macro.njk" import label %}
{% from "components/field/macro.njk" import field %}

<h2>Default</h2>
{% call field() %}
  {{ label({ for: "eesti-isikukood-input-demo", text: "Personal Identification Code" }) }}
  {{ eestiIsikukoodInput({ id: "eesti-isikukood-input-demo" }) }}
{% endcall %}

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>11 digits in the form GYYMMDDSSSC: G is sex and century (odd male, even female; 1-2 19th c., 3-4 20th c., 5-6 21st c.), SSS distinguishes persons born the same day, C is a checksum.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_identification_number#Estonia">Personal Identification Code</a>.</p>
